s to choose between upholding basic legal norms and maintaining Party order. In doing all of this, The Communist Judicial System in China, 1927-1976: Building on Fear fills a major lacuna in our understanding of communist-era China.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aJustice, Administration ofxHistoryy20th centuryzChina. 0aLawzChina -- 20th century -- History. 4aAsian Studies. 4aEast Asia and North East Asia. 4aHistory. 4aPolitics and Government. 7aLAW / Government / General.2bisacsh  aFear, Communist Judicial System, Mao's China.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074322708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2021 Englishz978311075409408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2021z9783110753868oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048554102zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048554102423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789048554102.jpg  a978-3-11-074322-7  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075409-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Law 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17S